defaultend the need for an 
defaultever growing list of 
defaultexemptions. It would introduce a standard which reflects the way low income households live in the 21
defaultst
default century.
default Furthermore, our research suggests that such a change may not result in the loss of savings an
defaultticipated by Government, and
default that
default the basis 
defaultfor the savings already claimed
